Grammar

    0 $accept: Program $end

    1 Program: CLASS IDENTIFIER LBRACE ProgramElements RBRACE

    2 ProgramElements: ε
    3                | ProgramElements MethodDecl
    4                | ProgramElements FieldDecl
    5                | ProgramElements SEMICOLON

    6 MethodDecl: PUBLIC STATIC MethodHeader MethodBody

    7 FieldDecl: PUBLIC STATIC Type IDENTIFIER IdList SEMICOLON
    8          | error SEMICOLON

    9 VarDecl: Type IDENTIFIER IdList SEMICOLON

   10 IdList: ε
   11       | IdList COMMA IDENTIFIER

   12 Type: BOOL
   13     | INT
   14     | DOUBLE

   15 MethodHeader: Type IDENTIFIER LPAR OptFormalParams RPAR
   16             | VOID IDENTIFIER LPAR OptFormalParams RPAR

   17 OptFormalParams: ε
   18                | FormalParams

   19 FormalParams: Type IDENTIFIER FormalParamsRest
   20             | STRING LSQ RSQ IDENTIFIER

   21 FormalParamsRest: ε
   22                 | FormalParamsRest COMMA Type IDENTIFIER

   23 MethodBody: LBRACE StatementAndVarDeclList RBRACE

   24 StatementAndVarDeclList: ε
   25                        | StatementAndVarDeclList Statement
   26                        | StatementAndVarDeclList VarDecl

   27 StatementList: ε
   28              | StatementList Statement

   29 Statement: LBRACE StatementList RBRACE
   30          | IF LPAR AExpr RPAR Statement
   31          | IF LPAR AExpr RPAR Statement ELSE Statement
   32          | WHILE LPAR AExpr RPAR Statement
   33          | RETURN OptExpr SEMICOLON
   34          | MethodInvocation SEMICOLON
   35          | Assignment SEMICOLON
   36          | ParseArgs SEMICOLON
   37          | PRINT LPAR ExprOrStrlit RPAR SEMICOLON
   38          | error SEMICOLON
   39          | SEMICOLON

   40 OptExpr: ε
   41        | AExpr

   42 ExprOrStrlit: AExpr
   43             | STRLIT

   44 MethodInvocation: IDENTIFIER LPAR OptExprList RPAR
   45                 | IDENTIFIER LPAR error RPAR

   46 OptExprList: ε
   47            | ExprList

   48 ExprList: AExpr
   49         | ExprList COMMA AExpr

   50 Assignment: IDENTIFIER ASSIGN AExpr

   51 AExpr: IDENTIFIER ASSIGN AExpr
   52      | Expr

   53 ParseArgs: PARSEINT LPAR IDENTIFIER LSQ AExpr RSQ RPAR
   54          | PARSEINT LPAR error RPAR

   55 Expr: Expr PLUS Expr
   56     | Expr MINUS Expr
   57     | Expr STAR Expr
   58     | Expr DIV Expr
   59     | Expr MOD Expr
   60     | Expr AND Expr
   61     | Expr OR Expr
   62     | Expr XOR Expr
   63     | Expr LSHIFT Expr
   64     | Expr RSHIFT Expr
   65     | Expr EQ Expr
   66     | Expr GE Expr
   67     | Expr GT Expr
   68     | Expr LE Expr
   69     | Expr LT Expr
   70     | Expr NE Expr
   71     | MINUS Expr
   72     | PLUS Expr
   73     | NOT Expr
   74     | LPAR AExpr RPAR
   75     | LPAR error RPAR
   76     | MethodInvocation
   77     | ParseArgs
   78     | IDENTIFIER OptDotLength
   79     | NATURAL
   80     | DECIMAL
   81     | BOOLLIT

   82 OptDotLength: ε
   83             | DOTLENGTH


